                    <b>Lego - Juniors - Knight''s Castle</b><br><br>Protect the King‚Äôs treasure hidden deep in the Knights‚Äô Castle!<br><br>The evil black knight is trying to steal the King‚Äôs treasure! Ride out with the brave King‚Äôs knight on his white horse and stop the bad guy before he topples the castle walls with his big catapult. Featuring Easy to Build models with lots of colourful Lego bricks, this iconic, castle-themed set has been specially designed for first-time brick builders. Your young knight will love to build and play with the set, and when it‚Äôs time for another build and play challenge, use the age-appropriate and inspiring building instructions to rebuild the Knights‚Äô Castle into an enemy tower or the King‚Äôs horse carriage using the extra bricks supplied with the set. The set also comes in an iconic, brick-shaped box that‚Äôs ideal for storing and transporting. <br><br><b>Features:</b><ul><li>Features Knights‚Äô Castle, a large catapult, small catapult and the knight‚Äôs horse</li><li>Knights‚Äô Castle features colourful, Easy to Build elements, big towers flags, a prison cell, small table, treasure chest with treasure and a spider, and various decorated elements</li><li>Accessories include a funny skeleton, crown, cup and a turkey bone</li><li>Weapons include a sword, crossbow and a spear</li><li>Also includes extra bricks for rebuilding the alternate models</li><li>Protect the King‚Äôs treasure!</li><li>Roll the large catapult into position and prepare to fire!</li><li>Return fire with the small catapult</li><li>Easy to Build elements are perfect for developing building skills</li><li>Includes age-appropriate building instructions</li><li>Rebuilds into an enemy tower or the King‚Äôs horse carriage</li><li>Lego Juniors sets are the perfect introduction to Lego brick building</li><li>Knights‚Äô Castle measures over 7‚Äù (19cm) high, 9‚Äù (25cm) wide and 4‚Äù (12cm) deep</li><li>Catapult base measures over 3‚Äù (8cm) long, 1‚Äù (5cm) wide and under 1‚Äù (3cm) high</li><li>King‚Äôs horse carriage measures over 3‚Äù (8cm) high, 5‚Äù (15cm) long and 2‚Äù (6cm) wide</li><li>Enemy tower measures over 5‚Äù (15cm) high, 2‚Äù (6cm) wide, 3‚Äù (8cm) deep</li></ul>
