                    <b>Hop aboard My First Train Set for beginning builder fun!</b><br><br>Introduce your child to the world of trains and building with the Lego Duplo My First Train Set. Create the colorful steam train with sound effects, a passenger wagon, station with ticket window, fueling pump and signal. With lots of Duplo bricks and more than 22 inches of track, it‚Äôs the perfect set for budding builders and hours of train-themed creative play. Includes train driver and child Duplo figures.<br><br><b>Features:</b><ul><li>Includes 2 Lego Duplo figures: train driver and child</li><li>Features a steam train with real sound effects, passenger wagon, station with ticket window and clock, fueling pump, signal, Duplo bricks and more than 22 inches of track</li><li>Duplo bricks include decorated bricks featuring flowers and a goat</li><li>Load the figures aboard the steam train and take a ride!</li><li>Fuel up the train and chug down the tracks!</li><li>Buy a ticket at the station</li><li>Tracks do not conduct electricity and therefore are not compatible with Lego 9V trains</li><li>For use with Duplo trains only</li><li>Duplo products are specially designed to be fun and safe for younger hands</li><li>Steam train measures over 3" (10cm) high, 5" (15cm) long and 2" (6cm) wide</li><li>Passenger wagon measures over 3" (10cm) high, 6" (16cm) long and 2" (6cm) wide</li><li>Train station measures over 7" (18cm) high, 7" (19cm) long and 2" (6cm) wide</li></ul>
