                    <b>Lego - Technic -  Service Truck</b><br><br>Build the lego Technic Service Truck and get to the rescue!<br><br>When a vehicle is stranded, make the rescue with the heavy-duty lego Technic Service Truck with tons of realistic powered functions. Activate the included lego Power Functions features to extend the rear outriggers or extend and raise the fully adjustable crane arm into position. Then lower the hook with the working winch, unfold the rear wheel lift and load a vehicle to tow. This awesome 2-in-1 Service Truck also features 8 wheels, all-wheel drive and hydraulic lifting element. It‚Äôs just like the real thing! Rebuilds into a truck with a crane that can raise and lower, grabber, outriggers and detachable trailer.<br><br><b>Features:</b><ul><li>Features lego Power Functions extending rear outriggers and extending wheel lift, fully adjustable crane arm and retractable winch</li><li>Also features 8 wheels, 4-wheel steering and a hydraulic element</li><li>Includes lego Power Functions motor and 8881 lego Power Functions Battery Box</li><li>2 models in 1: rebuilds into a truck with a crane that can raise and lower, grabber, outriggers and detachable trailer</li><li>Extend the outriggers for increased stability</li><li>Position the crane arm into place and lower the winch!</li><li>Attach the winch and tow vehicles</li><li>Extend the folding wheel lift</li><li>Building instructions only included for Service Truck. Please visit our online building instructions for the truck with a crane.</li><li>Measures over 5" (15cm) high, 17" (44cm) long and 5" (15cm) wide</li><li>Truck with trailer measures over 13" (34cm) high with crane up, 22" (57cm) long and 4" (11cm) wide</li></ul>
