                    <b>Lego - Technic - Construction Crew</b><br><br>Build your very own collection of detailed construction site vehicles!<br><br>Build a whole construction site of awesome scaled vehicles with the LEGO¬Æ Technic Construction Crew. This amazing set includes a Wheel Loader, a Dump Truck and an Excavator, each with a range of realistic, real world functions. The Excavator has a pivoting and articulating crane and 2 tough tracks, while the Wheel Loader has a lifting bucket and the Dump Truck has a tipping dump box to move heavy loads of earth. These are amazing models that will be a real test of your building skills and your imagination.<br><br><b>Features:</b><ul><li>Wheel Loader features articulated steering as well as a lifting and tipping bucket</li><li>Dump Truck features steering and a tipping dump box</li><li>Excavator features a turning superstructure, a highly flexible crane arm that can be used for a range of functions and twin tracks</li><li>Run the construction site with 3 cool vehicles</li><li>Enjoy testing your building skills and taking them to the next level</li><li>Go online for even more building inspiration at LEGO.com/technic<li>Wheel Loader measures over 5‚Äù (13cm) high, 8‚Äù (21cm) long and 3‚Äù (9cm) wide</li><li>Dump Truck measures over 3‚Äù (10cm) high, 7‚Äù (20cm) long and 2‚Äù (7cm) wide</li><li>Excavator measures over 6‚Äù (17cm) high, 8‚Äù (22cm) long and 4‚Äù (11cm) wide</li></ul>
